Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:21.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}思春期にかける手錠はないのだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:21.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}喜欢上一个人  是遗传因子设下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:26.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}欲望  其实早已启动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:31.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}各色各样的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}表里不一的纯情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:41.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}相互角力  胸口憋闷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:44.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}不要摸  让我摸  你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:48.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}打开  给我关上  要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:53.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}全神经顺从地坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}Love&Peace Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:58.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}我想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}想了解你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:08.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}我们的梦  请你许可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:11.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}我不需要什么爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:15.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}……还是给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:21.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fade(300,300)}青春  没有手铐能够束缚!
